name: Eisenhower Dr
description: The northern end of Eisenhower Drive, intersecting with Main Street. You are on Eisenhower Dr, at the intersection with Main St. To the north, Main St stretches out, a ribbon of charming commerce. Eisenhower Dr continues its quiet descent to the south, a testament to the town's growing prosperity. The air is a blend of distant traffic and the faint, sweet scent of blooming flowers.
